"Whoa" Cries Cliffjumper. He was hoping that Prowl wouldnt notice him. His
small frame collided with the talons of the beast, and sent him flying
backwards, straight onto his back. He lay motionless for a few seconds,
then strugled to sit up. He was gushing oil, and one of his eyes was
dangling from a spring. He strained himself to stand, and through much
pain, and anguish, stood up defiantly, "COME ON, you stupid freak" he
screamed, forgeting he was trying to save a life, and getting pissed. He
also forgot he wouldnt be able to take this thing on in hand to hand
combat...ever.
